### FH-Potsdam/steel-ant-input-output now has a Chat Room on Gitter

@fabiantheblind has just created a chat room. You can visit it here: [https://gitter.im/FH-Potsdam/steel-ant-input-output](https://gitter.im/FH-Potsdam/steel-ant-input-output?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge&content=body_link).

This pull-request adds this badge to your README.md:


[![Gitter](https://badges.gitter.im/Join%20Chat.svg)](https://gitter.im/FH-Potsdam/steel-ant-input-output?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge&utm_content=body_badge)

If my aim is a little off, please [let me know](https://github.com/gitterHQ/readme-badger/issues).

Happy chatting.


PS: [Click here](https://gitter.im/settings/badger/opt-out) if you would prefer not to receive automatic pull-requests from Gitter in future.
